    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1921-05-27T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1921-05-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="362"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d362">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">812.01/7½</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Under Secretary of State</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Fletcher</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-05-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 27, 1921</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Dear Mr. Secretary</hi>: I have just talked with Mr. Norman
                        Davis<note n="45" xml:id="d362fn45">Alberto J. Pani, Mexican Secretary of
                        Foreign Affairs.</note> over the telephone. He informed me that the
                    understanding with the British Embassy with regard to Mexico was as follows:</p>
                <p>That in view of pressure which was being brought to bear on the British
                    Government to recognize Mexico, that Government had decided not to recognize
                    until we should do so; that we would keep them advised of any important steps
                    which we might take looking toward recognition, in order that British action
                    might follow ours.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>H[<hi rend="smallcaps">enry</hi>] P. F[<hi rend="smallcaps"
                        >letcher</hi>]</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
